{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView","doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView\/TextView","doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView\/TextView\/NSTextInputClient-Implementations"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Returns the fraction of the distance from the left side of the character to the right side that a given point","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"lies."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"for","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"point","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSPoint","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The point to test.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"point"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The fraction of the distance aPoint is through the glyph in which it lies. May be 0 or 1 if aPoint","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"is not within the bounding rectangle of a glyph (0 if the point is to the left or above the glyph;"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"1 if it’s to the right or below)."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For purposes such as dragging out a selection or placing the insertion point, a partial percentage less than or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"equal to 0.5 indicates that aPoint should be considered as falling before the glyph; a partial percentage"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"greater than 0.5 indicates that it should be considered as falling after the glyph. If the nearest glyph doesn’t","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"lie under aPoint at all (for example, if aPoint is beyond the beginning or end of a line), this ratio is 0 or 1.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, if the glyph stream contains the glyphs “A” and “b”, with the width of “A” being 13 points, and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"aPoint is 8 points from the left side of “A”, then the fraction of the distance is 8\/13, or 0.615. In this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"case, the aPoint should be considered as falling between “A” and “b” for purposes such as dragging out a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"selection or placing the insertion point."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"for"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSPoint","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV"}],"modules":[{"name":"AuroraEditorTextView"}],"extendedModule":"AuroraEditorTextView","externalID":"c:@CM@AuroraEditorTextView@objc(cs)TextView(im)fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyphForPoint:","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)","symbolKind":"method"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/auroraeditortextview\/textview\/fractionofdistancethroughglyph(for:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView\/TextView\/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)"},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://AuroraEditorTextView/documentation/AuroraEditorTextView/TextView/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns the fraction of the distance from the left side of the character to the right side that a given point"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"lies."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"for"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSPoint","text":"NSPoint"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:14CoreFoundation7CGFloatV","text":"CGFloat","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"title":"fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)","identifier":"doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView\/TextView\/fractionOfDistanceThroughGlyph(for:)","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/auroraeditortextview\/textview\/fractionofdistancethroughglyph(for:)"},"doc://AuroraEditorTextView/documentation/AuroraEditorTextView/TextView":{"title":"TextView","url":"\/documentation\/auroraeditortextview\/textview","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"TextView","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A view that draws and handles user interactions with text.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Optimized for line-based documents, does not attempt to have feature parity with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NSTextView"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/AuroraEditorTextView\/documentation\/AuroraEditorTextView\/TextView","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"key